---
// ContactInfo.astro
---
<div class="contact-info">
  <div class="contact-info-top">
    <span class="col-label">Contato</span>
    <h1>Vamos conversar sobre seu projeto.</h1>
    <p>Preencha o formulário e me conta o que você tem em mente. Sem compromisso — só uma conversa para entender se faz sentido trabalharmos juntos.</p>

    <div class="contact-details">
      <div class="contact-detail">
        <span class="detail-label">E-mail</span>
        <a href="mailto:pedro@cordeirolima.net" class="detail-value">pedro@cordeirolima.net</a>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-detail">
        <span class="detail-label">Localização</span>
        <span class="detail-value">Hortolândia, SP — atendo remotamente</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="contact-info-bottom">
    <div class="availability">
      <div class="availability-dot"></div>
      <span>Disponível para novos projetos</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .contact-info {
    padding: 96px 80px;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(26, 25, 22, 0.08);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .col-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-stone);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    display: block;
  }

  .contact-info h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--color-obsidian);
  }

  .contact-info p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-stone);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 380px;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  .contact-details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .contact-detail {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .detail-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-stone);
  }

  .detail-value {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-obsidian);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  a.detail-value:hover {
    color: var(--color-stone);
  }

  .contact-info-bottom {
    margin-top: 64px;
  }

  .availability {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .availability-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-grove);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .availability span {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-stone);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  /* Tablet: 768px – 1024px */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .contact-info {
      padding: 72px 40px;
    }
    .contact-info h1 {
      font-size: 38px;
    }
  }

  /* Mobile: até 767px */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .contact-info {
      padding: 56px 24px;
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(26, 25, 22, 0.08);
    }
    .contact-info h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
    }
    .contact-info p {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
